# Optional: free Alpha Vantage API key for willBB markets data. Falls back
# gracefully (Yahoo + Stooq + synthetic) if absent. Get a free key at
# https://www.alphavantage.co/support/#api-key — free tier is 25 requests
# per day so we cache aggressively and only call it when Yahoo fails.
ALPHA_VANTAGE_API_KEY=

# Otherwise the portfolio is a static site — no database, no auth, no
# other API keys required. Deploy as a standard Next.js app on Vercel or
# any Node host.
